        "ggl0NxBI-r8_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\"><strong>How To Use Your SerlinoLab Self-Tanning Drops</strong></span>",
        "ggoh5KeK7tb_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">How to use them, how often, and how to get a natural colour without looking like you tried</span>",
        "ggYDtkSA8ZA_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DL3cU1C3DUE",
        "ggYDtkSA8ZA_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/1095883398",
        "ggYDtkSA8ZA_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/2cd3deb506b54b009063f7270ab5cf2e.mp4",
        "ggYDtkSA8ZA_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/4._website_thumbnail_self-tanning.webp",
        "gg1y1k4TLtc_text": "<strong>How To Use Them</strong>",
        "ggM5c85gwEt_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/2.webp",
        "ggM5c85gwEt_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3.webp",
        "ggArbEE5QNG_text": "Use them at night — not in the morning",
        "gg9MJALFpNT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3.webp",
        "gganb4ETLPU_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\"><strong>Use them at night — not in the morning</strong></span>",
        "ggI1nXJ9-LF_text": "<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">The drops need 6–8 hours to develop. Apply them before bed and let them work while you sleep.</span>",
        "ggaVbZ0svvS_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/1_d45369cb-dc28-4f09-b9c0-2fc1618ac549.webp",
        "ggaVbZ0svvS_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/2.webp",
        "ggvNtz_Zzwi_text": "Don't mix with your night cream",
        "ggNLiZyoaiB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/2.webp",
        "ggkj5k6OuQe_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>Don't mix with your night cream</strong></span>",
        "ggtnJ1NQHgu_text": "<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">The night cream contains Retinyl Palmitate. Mixing them can cause irritation and uneven development. On nights you use the drops, skip the night cream. Cleanse, apply the drops, go to bed.</span>",
        "ggxNsKpoSDU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3.webp",
        "ggxNsKpoSDU_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_22.webp",
        "gghcfB2hOZT_text": "How much",
        "ggFg_OXTC6p_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_22.webp",
        "ggxujJ1DGpq_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>How much</strong></span>",
        "ggmVplSz10k_text": "<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">2–3 drops mixed into your regular moisturiser in the palm of your hand. Blend together, then apply evenly to your face, neck, and jawline.</span><br>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">One bottle lasts around 30 days — more or less depending on how often you apply and how much colour you want.</span>",
        "ggf6iYjD79e_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3.webp",
        "ggf6iYjD79e_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_20.webp",
        "ggq-GTtAeFx_text": "How often",
        "ggxWR4THRcy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/Serlino_Lab_20.webp",
        "ggN1upZ9Ekk_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>How often</strong></span>",
        "ggJZXEE3Zjb_text": "<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Start every 2–3 nights. That's enough to build colour without overdoing it. Once you see where you land, adjust — more frequent if you want darker, less if the result already works for you. Find what works and stick with it.</span>",
        "ggUXjSIs8Lw_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">What To Expect</span>",
        "ggJkbrWCf47_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/30ml_Self_Tanning_Creative_render_1.0.webp",
        "ggEEL3r9OyE_text": "You apply at night, go to bed. In the morning you wash your face as normal — the colour stays. You go from pale to having actual colour.&nbsp;<br><br>Not a tan from a beach holiday, but a healthy, natural tone that makes you look like you're doing fine.<br>&nbsp;That colour holds for 2–3 days. Then it starts to fade. That's when you reapply.<br>&nbsp;No smell. No transfer on the pillow. No one knows why you look better — they just do."
      }
